tool_description: JoJ Web Search API. Search the world's information, including webpages, related keywords and more.
name: JoJ Web Search
title: JoJ Web Search

api_list.name: Search

required_parameters.name: query
required_parameters.description:
Search query. You can use Google Search parameters.

e.g. `adele site:youtube.com`
e.g. `harry potter filetype:pdf`
e.g. `inurl:store`
e.g. `ronaldo -cristiano`

optional_parameters.name: related_keywords
optional_parameters.description:
Shows related keywords. Default: `false`

*Entering `true`, increases API latency*

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description: Max results number. Max recommended value is `300`.
